{"tid":386070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MK男遇PTU截查　誤按噴劑噴自己","createTime":"2017-09-03T15:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T16:18:05.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b691036da0232536f0422239340cfc47d8401c7","tid":386070,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170903/large/1504442649_b685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170903%2Flarge%2F1504442649_b685.jpg&h=bfad636d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚上7時許，PTU警員於旺角奶路臣街10號對開巡邏，其間截查一名形迹可疑男子，在其身上搜出一支噴劑。該名男子聲稱購自淘寶，混亂間誤將噴劑向自己噴灑，他感覺不適，事後由救護車送院檢查。警方撿走噴劑，調查是否「胡椒噴霧」。"},{"pid":"3749292e978d7cf2a67d1969b438a640d34bd76a","tid":386070,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170903&amp;guid=57165161&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170903%26guid%3D57165161%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=t9FZl5ZevfK5fzMtLmZ%2F8gCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ebcdff19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170903%26guid%3D57165161%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=00d71dea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170903&amp;guid=57165161&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"704c707f76ae877f9124e6bbc9078874e3f61d17","tid":386070,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://giphy.com/gifs/fail-graffiti-grafittiart-fGwduZVZfRdqo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com%2Fgifs%2Ffail-graffiti-grafittiart-fGwduZVZfRdqo&h=d7